<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a17Nov1932"><font color="red">17 November 1932</font> <i>NLSP</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Carolus Verhulst of the Servire Press): I beg to acknowledge receipt of your letters addressed to me concerning the fragment Mr Joyce is publishing in the coming number of Transition &hellip; forwarded your letters to Mr Pinker &hellip; I hope he will find his way to arrange for a publication of a deluxe edition as planned by you. </div>
